721a68501894d56451f5a5f0f1301","tid":2421493,"uid":165385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c7afc6a4a3fc7cc073e14b5943df188217d5de","tid":2421493,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6a283547414d280369120ce260a7ec4bfffaf3","tid":2421493,"uid":49312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ebe805a4e27f8a52d854edae300c20338616ab80","tid":2421493,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:01:05.000Z","msg":"前年7月14日在沙田新城市廣場咬斷警長手指的杜啟華，今日被裁定有意圖而傷人等四項罪名成立，即時還柙，預計於三月中判刑。杜媽媽聞訊後落淚，手裡一直緊緊掐著紙巾，由親友攙扶著她步出法庭。<br />\n<br />\n杜啟華今天穿一套深藍色西裝應訊，臨入庭前與兩位友人相擁。兩人是他在港大舍堂的「堂友」，接受訪問但不願具名。他們回想對杜啟華的第一印象，都覺得這人傻乎乎的，平易近人；認識久了，就發現他很有正義感，即使在舍堂內也會為不同事情發聲。<br />\n<br />\n案件於今日下午2時半在西九龍裁判法院頒下裁決，許多杜啟華的大學好友、中學同學都前來旁聽支持，也有滿頭白髮的婆婆、「旁聽師」，還有今早在同一個法庭進行了第三天審訊的7.28上環暴動案被告等。旁聽大約逾30人，坐滿了公眾席、延伸法庭，不少人只能在法庭外的走道等待。<br />\n<br />\n杜啟華在庭外與好友們相擁，直到馬上要開庭，才小跑步入內。法庭的門閉上，法官陳仲衡步出，隨即宣讀裁決，裁定四項罪名成立，杜啟華須即時還柙。<br />\n<br />\n前一刻才與杜啟華相擁的兩位「堂友」，雖早已有心理準備他會被還柙，已「道別」過了，但被問到得悉裁決時的感受，二人仍語塞良久，表示不太懂得形容那刻心情。惟他們說，知道杜啟華不希望別人擔心自己，與杜談過入獄後的事，但杜總是輕輕帶過，一副輕鬆的模樣。「啊，佢想入到去教其他囚友整甜品」、「佢想做廚房，整啲好嘢俾其他人食」。<br />\n<br />\n杜啟華讀食物營養（food nutrition），更是烹飪能手。二人透露，他甚麼都識煮，中餐、西餐、甜品&hellip;&hellip;最喜歡他烹調的南瓜湯。杜啟華不僅在宿舍煮飯，更會邀請朋友上他家食飯。二人又記得，杜啟華喜歡卡比獸，睡房整張牀都放滿了卡比獸公仔，「因為好似佢，（眼睛）係一條線。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38500/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E6%9D%9C%E5%95%9F%E8%8F%AF-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E6%96%B7%E6%8C%87%E6%A1%88-38500/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F38500%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E6%259D%259C%25E5%2595%259F%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25A1%2588-38500%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8J2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=86cf5836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38500/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E6%9D%9C%E5%95%9F%E8%8F%AF-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E6%96%B7%E6%8C%87%E6%A1%88-38500/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:36:35.000Z","msg":"多謝你嘅付出，多謝你"},{"pid":"bd60cc4f9191e42452fdf978d8796ba6196a0b7f","tid":2421493,"uid":96909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"手joke<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34eba9fbcf76c18816b42662b55ec2be3abc57b","tid":2421493,"uid":209978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6e5fb63ae054cf163e3ae54267a1daa20dad7b","tid":2421493,"uid":315376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3dcd2af2c5fcf8f06dd0a71954d6895575f40600","tid":2421493,"uid":38528,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"識佢,公開試衰左,發奮讀asso升返上HKU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T16:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class